rows.label: campfev11_190_150_msg0001
rows.name:
Perhaps we should investigate Trigo
a little more...?

rows.label: campfev11_190_150_msg0002
rows.name:
I'd like to do something to mark the
graves of these poor people...
Not just mother's...

rows.label: campfev11_190_150_msg0003
rows.name: Of course Laura. Let's do it.

rows.label: campfev11_190_150_msg0004
rows.name:
Milt, Hikari, and I will be honored
to help you with that.

rows.label: campfev11_190_150_msg0006
rows.name: "Honored" is kind of a strong word.

rows.label: campfev11_190_150_msg0010
rows.name:
Uh...
Hey. I'll help. No worries. None.

rows.label: campfev11_190_150_msg0011
rows.name:
Nice to see everyone's feeling so...
community spirited. I'm impressed!

rows.label: campfev11_190_150_msg0012
rows.name: OK! Let's head back to Trigo.
